    {
      "chinese": "建築聚會所、房屋、瞭望台、牛舍、倉庫、廚房都是就地取材，如木材、竹子、茅草和藤條。用什麼木材為柱為樑呢？用什麼竹子為牆為房頂？怎麼用藤條綁住才牢固？這些都是當時部落男子重要的學習課題之一，我們不可以忘記，以免這些老人家建造房子的技能消失。",
      "ab": "O sapatireng to sefi, loma’, pikacawan, pakolongan, cokep, demi’ no Pangcah/’Amis, saheto o kilang, o ’aol, o eli’ ato ’oway ko sapipatireng. Ona sapisimsim mikilim ato mipili’, o taneng no to’as konini. O maan a kilang ko malohecek ato malofalat? O maan a ’aolan ko malodayna? Maanen ko pifalod ta makedec tanektek? \r\n[===]\r\nMaemin mateli mana’ang i fongoh no mato’asay. Onini saheto o papalifeten no mita a minanam a mifana’. Aka tawalen no mita, ta caay ka lasawad ko fenek no to’as a patireng to loma’.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2021/03/03/1b009afab1dab3f8143d5ad572113022.wav",
